@startuml Fabio_Investment_Flows_Data_Flow
!theme spacelab
title Fabio's Investment Flows - Backend Template Data Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E8F5E8
    BorderColor #388E3C
    FontColor #000000
}

skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    BorderColor #1976D2
    FontColor #000000
}

' Backend Template Architecture Flow
package "Backend Template Architecture" {
    
    component [Backend API] as API
    component [Product Data] as PD
    component [StringToken Content] as STC
    component [Metadata Structure] as MS
    component [Styling Information] as SI
    
    component [StringToken Parser] as STP
    component [Value Extraction] as VE
    component [Style Mapping] as SM
    component [Typography Resolution] as TR
    
    component [Metadata Processor] as MP
    component [Field Mapping] as FM
    component [Section Generation] as SG
    component [Content Organization] as CO
    
    component [Dynamic Content Generator] as DCG
    component [UI Component Builder] as UCB
    component [Layout Manager] as LM
    component [Template Engine] as TE
    
    component [Rendered UI] as RUI
    component [Dynamic Labels] as DL
    component [Styled Text] as ST
    component [Organized Sections] as OS
    component [Interactive Elements] as IE
}

' Data Flow
API --> STP : "Raw StringToken Data"
note right: {"value": "Investment Title", "style": "header1"}

STP --> MP : "Parsed StringWithTypograph"
note right: StringWithTypograph(value: "Investment Title", typograph: .header1)

MP --> DCG : "Processed Metadata"
note right: [Field(label: "Amount", value: "R$ 1.000,00")]

DCG --> RUI : "Dynamic UI Components"
note right: Styled labels, organized sections, interactive elements

' Backend Template Benefits
note top of API
  **Backend Template Benefits:**
  
  ✅ **Dynamic Content**: Backend controls all text and styling
  ✅ **A/B Testing**: Easy content experimentation
  ✅ **Rapid Iteration**: Changes without app updates
  ✅ **Consistency**: Unified styling across flows
  ✅ **Localization**: Multi-language support
  ✅ **Performance**: Optimized rendering
end note

' StringToken System Details
note right of STP
  **StringToken System:**
  
  **Input Format:**
  ```json
  {
    "value": "Investment Amount",
    "style": "body1"
  }
  ```
  
  **Processing:**
  1. Extract value and style
  2. Map style to PurchaseTypograph
  3. Create StringWithTypograph object
  4. Apply typography rules
end note

' Metadata Processing Details
note right of MP
  **Metadata Processing:**
  
  **Input Structure:**
  ```json
  {
    "metadatas": [
      {
        "label": {"value": "Amount", "style": "body1"},
        "value": {"value": "R$ 1.000,00", "style": "title3"}
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
  
  **Processing:**
  1. Parse metadata arrays
  2. Generate field mappings
  3. Create section layouts
  4. Organize content structure
end note

' Dynamic Content Generation
note right of DCG
  **Dynamic Content Generation:**
  
  **Features:**
  - Build UI components from metadata
  - Apply backend-controlled styling
  - Support A/B testing variations
  - Optimize performance
  - Handle complex layouts
  
  **Output:**
  - Styled text components
  - Organized sections
  - Interactive elements
  - Responsive layouts
end note

' Rendered UI Features
note right of RUI
  **Rendered UI Features:**
  
  **Dynamic Elements:**
  - Backend-controlled text
  - Dynamic styling
  - Organized sections
  - Interactive components
  
  **Benefits:**
  - Consistent user experience
  - Easy content updates
  - A/B testing support
  - Multi-language support
  - Performance optimization
end note

' System Architecture Benefits
note bottom
  **System Architecture Benefits:**
  
  **Backend Template Architecture:**
  - 🎯 **Dynamic Content**: Backend controls all content and styling
  - 🧪 **A/B Testing**: Easy experimentation without app updates
  - ⚡ **Rapid Iteration**: Content changes without app store releases
  - 🎨 **Consistency**: Unified styling across all investment flows
  - 🌍 **Localization**: Multi-language support through backend configuration
  - 🚀 **Performance**: Optimized rendering and caching
  
  **VIP Architecture:**
  - 🏗️ **Clean Architecture**: Clear separation of concerns
  - 🧪 **Testability**: Easy to test and mock components
  - 🔧 **Maintainability**: Easy to maintain and extend
  - 📈 **Scalability**: Scales with application growth
  - 🔒 **Security**: Built-in security and privacy protection
  
  **Navigation & Coordination:**
  - 🧭 **Flexible Navigation**: Coordinator pattern for complex flows
  - 🔗 **Deep Linking**: Comprehensive deep linking support
  - 📱 **Flow Management**: Seamless user experience
  - 🔧 **Dependency Injection**: Loose coupling and testability
end note

@enduml
